<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 18:24:55 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>探秘苔藓世界</title><link>https://some.pics/69e7c0f464254</link><description>&lt;p&gt;深入苔藓之中...&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A flight of steps made of flat stone slabs leads through moss and trees to a clearing covered in moss. " height="2870" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/69e7c0f464254.jpg" width="2151"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 18:24:55 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>迪士尼旧照重现</title><link>https://some.pics/69e7b1eda63be</link><description>&lt;p&gt;开始扫描旧底片时，发现了这张2000年在华特迪士尼世界拍的照片。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A large iconic Disney character hand with a white glove reaches upward toward a red serpentine ribbon and star, set against the geometric sphere structure of Epcot Center. Visitors walk in the plaza below on a sunny day with blue skies and white clouds." height="3764" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mihobu/69e7b1eda63be.jpg" width="2509"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mihobu.some.pics"&gt;@mihobu&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 17:20:50 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Metamonada CAZymes热图</title><link>https://some.pics/69e72fa45ab97</link><description>&lt;p&gt;选定CAZymes在Metamonada谱系中的注释热图。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Annotated heatmap of select CAZymes across Metamonada lineages." height="4050" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roach/69e72fa45ab97.png" width="7200"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roach.some.pics"&gt;@roach&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 08:04:55 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>印第安泉州立公园小瀑布</title><link>https://some.pics/69e673e737a82</link><description>&lt;p&gt;印第安泉州立公园溢洪道下方的一处小瀑布。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A small waterfall cascades over dark, jagged rocks surrounded by lush green foliage. A fallen log rests on the rocks, adding texture to the scene." height="5472" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/69e673e737a82.jpg" width="3648"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 18:43:54 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>宁静时刻</title><link>https://some.pics/69e66caae8e50</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一个更平静的时刻。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A huge raindrop on a green leaf. A mint leaf, slightly blurred, in front." height="3286" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/69e66caae8e50.jpg" width="1850"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 18:13:01 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>